{"tid":605252,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"講真mk成身排骨操到有少少腹肌就扮大隻好噁心","createTime":"2018-03-25T13:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T13:22:57.000Z","uid":35587,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29991356b916c50d2455ef453b5146eb441db23b","tid":605252,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"bc0cd78d7c69b2de05ac30e54b56e1ffd84b9d15","tid":605252,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bb17aa8dc93cfb9a0700cdec6161ebb8eeaabb9","tid":605252,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"袓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4be82b846dd313f8b02020185e8f6671018e884","tid":605252,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bb17aa8dc93cfb9a0700cdec6161ebb8eeaabb9","tid":605252,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"袓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53261b2f039a66eb843635709dfd4eec017e1b8","tid":605252,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc0cd78d7c69b2de05ac3